# Line-ending normalization — every clone (local, Cowork, CI) agrees, so the
# daily reasoning-layer commits don't carry phantom CRLF churn.
# Text files are stored and checked out as LF; Windows scripts stay CRLF.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.bat   text eol=crlf
*.cmd   text eol=crlf
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.pdf   binary
*.xlsx  binary
*.xlsm  binary
